description:
Alibaba's instant messaging and trading tool tailored for transactions on Taobao and 1688

AliIM is an instant messaging and trading tool tailored for transactions on Taobao and 1688, which contains instant messaging, file transfer, multi-person voice and video chat, app center and transaction assistant, etc., providing buyers with convenient, safe and brand-new shopping and communication experience.
source: 阿里巴巴（中国）有限公司
